        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2376424968" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9510328620185617009">This book was recommended to me by a friend and I went in with extremely low expectations so I was surprised when it turned out quite decent.<br/> It&apos;s actually a short novella so I read it in one sitting. The story is sweet, funny at times and simple ( although you can read more into it ). <br/>All in all very entertaining and I would recommend it.</span>
  <span id="freeText9510328620185617009" style="display:none">This book was recommended to me by a friend and I went in with extremely low expectations so I was surprised when it turned out quite decent.<br /> It's actually a short novella so I read it in one sitting. The story is sweet, funny at times and simple ( although you can read more into it ). <br />All in all very entertaining and I would recommend it.</span>
