        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was ok"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was ok</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Mass Market Paperback 9782864245049" href="/book/show/1809608.Le_vieux_qui_lisait_des_romans_d_amour">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/25128624-nicole?shelf=dispo-bu-droit-lettres">dispo-bu-droit-lettres</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/25128624-nicole?shelf=club-de-lecture-2016-17">club-de-lecture-2016-17</a>, 
